{
  "stem": "25938.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I put the thermometer-- thermometer on here-- here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he would-- and he says-- this SS man said to us, stay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'll be back soon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we all stayed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They stayed. 12-- about 12 people, 10, 12 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly but a group of people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "At that time, I took the thermometer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I saw I had the Fahrenheit was more than normal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I don't know how-- how much at that time was-- was-- it was normal, but I know it was-- it was above.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I said to myself, that-- that is not good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That-- that means that that group will be sent-- sent to the-- to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So what I did was I took the jacket.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I threw out-- threw out the thermometer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I ran.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So imagine all the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "A few hundred people in that-- in that maybe 200 or 300 people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to the-- to the-- to the barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I figured I couldn't go in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See, but I-- I had to go with that group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what'd I do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said to myself, I'll wait till they will come to the march back, and I'll sneak in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, the whole people to the [? barrack. ?] That's what I did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I succeeded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] When we-- we are young, we are-- if I-- if I was older, 10, 20 years older, I wouldn't have done that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at that time I was young.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- so I-- I ran.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went-- when I was running, I thought the whole-- the whole [INAUDIBLE] people run after me, that the whole world is running-- is running after me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Imagine, ?] I broke the rule.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I didn't think-- I didn't think of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
